name: PhoenixCityGuide
0:
”Alexa, open Phoenix city guide”
”Alexa, ask Phoenix city guide for the top five”
”Alexa, ask phoenix city guide to tell me the local news”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: phoenix city guide
des: This skill is a guide to the city of Phoenix Arizona. You can ask your Amazon Echo for local news, attractions, and the top five things to do in Phoenix. This skill will help a visitor to the city, or someone who lives in Phoenix who wants to find new things to do. For news headlines, the skill gets its information from the New York Times.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
